    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small and light round shields carried by medieval foot soldiers to protect themselves in battle. The reduced size allowed soldiers to move freely and swiftly.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
